Name: Bunny Hop : Eggstreme
About the game: Bunny Hop : Eggstreme is a 3D platformer based on strafing, surfing, and many more unique movement mechanics. Beat your own records or your friends on the leaderboard, collect hidden easter eggs, run through biome-themed levels. Play online with your friends or alone, find new routes or just enjoy the view. Features Bunny Hop Multiplayer Replays Global leaderboards Customization Easter eggs More than 20 different levels New maps every month A lot of fun Join us on Discord !
